eic.beike.projectx.android.activities

Class GameActivity

  • java.lang.Object
    • Activity
      • eic.beike.projectx.android.activities.GameActivity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MessageDialog.MessageDialogListener

    public class GameActivity
extends Activity
implements MessageDialog.MessageDialogListener
    The GameActivity initiates the game, sends user input to the model and lets the model update the view. This class also registers the score and switch activity once the round is over. This is something of a god object but Android feels geared towards fat activities.
    Author:
    Mikael, Adam, Alex, Simon
